{"data":{"properties":{"created_at":1631567851000,"events":{},"identifier":"stores/prefersscheme","modified_at":1631567851000,"properties":{},"sections":[{"identifier":"prefersscheme","level":1,"text":"prefersscheme"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"built-in-shortcuts","level":2,"text":"Built-in Shortcuts"},{"identifier":"compatibility","level":2,"text":"Compatibility"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"prefersscheme-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Code,\n        Heading,\n        Text,\n        prefersscheme,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n\n    const darkmode_store = prefersscheme(\"dark\");\n    const lightmode_store = prefersscheme(\"light\");\n</script>\n\n<Heading>User Color Scheme Preferences</Heading>\n\n<Text>\n    Darkmode: <Code>{$darkmode_store}</Code>\n</Text>\n\n<Text>\n    Lightmode: <Code>{$lightmode_store}</Code>\n</Text>","syntax":"svelte","title":"prefersscheme Preview"},{"identifier":"prefersscheme-imports","script":"import {\n    prefersscheme,\n    prefersdark,\n    preferslight,\n} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";","syntax":"javascript","title":"prefersscheme Imports"},{"identifier":"prefersscheme-shortcuts","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Code,\n        Heading,\n        Text,\n        prefersdark,\n        preferslight,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n\n    const darkmode_store = prefersdark();\n    const lightmode_store = preferslight();\n</script>\n\n<Heading>User Color Scheme Preferences</Heading>\n\n<Text>\n    Darkmode: <Code>{$darkmode_store}</Code>\n</Text>\n\n<Text>\n    Lightmode: <Code>{$lightmode_store}</Code>\n</Text>","syntax":"svelte","title":"prefersscheme Shortcuts"}],"title":"prefersscheme"},"render":"<h1 id=\"prefersscheme\">prefersscheme</h1>\n<p><code>prefersscheme</code> is a <a href=\"https://svelte.dev/docs#svelte_store\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Svelte Store</a>, which returns <code>true</code> whenever <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><code>matchMedia(SCHEME)</code></a> is validated.</p>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Change your Operating System's color settings to see changes.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/stores/prefersscheme/prefersscheme-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/stores/prefersscheme/prefersscheme-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    prefersscheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    prefersdark<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    preferslight<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><h2 id=\"built-in-shortcuts\">Built-in Shortcuts</h2>\n<p>The <code>prefersscheme</code> Store also comes with two preconfigured default shortcuts, <code>prefersdark</code> and <code>preferslight</code>.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/stores/prefersscheme/prefersscheme-shortcuts?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/stores/prefersscheme/prefersscheme-shortcuts?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"compatibility\">Compatibility</h2>\n<p>The Store is dependent on <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><code>Window.matchMedia</code></a>. So if you're rendering on the server, it'll always return <code>false</code>.</p>\n"}}